<p>12 May 2015.</p>
<p><em>Madame Butterfly.</em> By Giacomo Puccini. LA SCALA, Milan, Italy. 17 February 1904.</p>
<p><em>Miss Saigon.</em> Music and Lyrics by Claude-Michel Schonberg and Richard Maltby.</p>
<p>Written by Claude-Michel Schonberg and Alain Boublil. WEST END, London. 1989.</p>
<p>Rohmer, Sax. <em>The Mystery of Dr. Fu-Manchu</em>. UK: Methuen, 1913.</p>
<p><em>Seeking Asian Female</em>. Dir. Debbie Lum. South by Southwest Film Festival, 2012.</p>
<p><em>South Pacific.</em> Music and Lyrics by Richard Rodgers and Oscar Hammerstein II. Written</p>
<p>by Oscar Hammerstein II and Joshua Logan. BROADWAY, New York. 1949.</p>
<p>Stefani, Gwen. (2004). <em>Harajuku Girls</em>. On <em>Love. Angel. Music. Baby.</em> [CD]. United</p>
<p>States: Interscope.</p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->
	
